{"tid":2088124,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美眾議員麥高文：美國與國際社會必須採取強烈行動去幫助港人和令中國政府負責","createTime":"2020-07-01T03:58:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-01T04:25:30.000Z","uid":92301,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"34f10695af9e949ed19a5738e1d96c11776ea285","tid":2088124,"uid":92301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T03:58:06.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://twitter.com/RepMcGovern/status/1278005190059266050?s=19\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FRepMcGovern%2Fstatus%2F1278005190059266050%3Fs%3D19&d=oa%2BbSijZO%2BDWYSsAyiffbom5R6Uo%2BMV3ZOx7awwfaZg%3D&h=1e3fbc62\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FRepMcGovern%2Fstatus%2F1278005190059266050%3Fs%3D19&h=1f845ff1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/RepMcGovern/status/1278005190059266050?s=19</a>"},{"pid":"4c1174aca5df36550c71125c71fadd47591b3612","tid":2088124,"uid":121146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T03:59:08.000Z","msg":"廢侵：嬲嬲 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n完"},{"pid":"4b25d8609d6a1c271a84c280df01fa431c70facd","tid":2088124,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T03:59:19.000Z","msg":"麻煩你夾實biden <img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d4dce646e240f075ab7ca6cdbbf38b66859e6e6","tid":2088124,"uid":110509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T04:04:35.000Z","msg":"retweet"},{"pid":"ca3c749e90d535e8826b2bb06adb8f5b318ad98a","tid":2088124,"uid":304769,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T04:10:29.000Z","msg":"無錯，咪比放負五毛影響啦，大家<br />\n<br />\n借個位<br />\n正視聽：若抗爭方向不隨局勢改變，只會無謂地損兵折將<br />\n香港街頭抗爭目標，亦都係街頭抗爭最大效果；&ldquo;攬炒&rdquo;已經達到，今次搞蟈安法其實仲攬炒過上年出老解。<br />\n宜家<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">跟著落黎就係引導全球政府同議會（尤其美國）做野</span></strong>，所以大家重點應該著眼帶出清晰民意授權比各國政府做野，畫面靚+全球廣泛報導（類似反蟈安法銅鑼灣自由行）係最理想，用選票帶出民意亦十分重要。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">大家要小心五毛、熱普城共諜放負風向：美國唔會幫我地（舊年年尾）-》英國係廢國無用架（今年年頭）-》歐盟奶共唔會幫我地、美國制裁無用（宜家）</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n大家要記住，香港生路只有一條：救香港人+攬炒促進支爆+重建香港。<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">沒有支爆，香港獨立或者歸英等重建方案全部都係痴人說夢。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n未來幾個月至支共瓦解期間大家要做嘅事：1.<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">走資</span></strong>2.全球救生艇<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">救手足加有細路既黃絲家庭</span></strong>（細路是重點，香港未來棟樑，正如今時今日d前線義士，咪比佢地洗腦變小糞紅，否則香港係真正玩完）3.比足夠<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">民意授權，敦促美國以至各國停止外匯流入香港</span></strong>，包括但不限於：禁止美國個人或公司投資港股、債券，暫停接受香港用美元結算等等4.最後就真係等<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>支那自己爆</strong></span>"},{"pid":"7d07948990e929f53e468b02f391fed81583da50","tid":2088124,"uid":126305,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T04:23:13.000Z","msg":"做野未呀仆街"},{"pid":"a0c329fe9970efb47e2f7f23e40b5f0377722396","tid":2088124,"uid":205884,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T04:23:29.000Z","msg":"I am proud to stand with hk<br />\n呢句先係重點<br />\n甘迺迪起柏林圍牆前講<br />\n&ldquo;i take pride in the words ich bin ein Berliner&rdquo;"},{"pid":"f257ff29d25d3fa5e6e0c4b1a8ab16f0e011bfdf","tid":2088124,"uid":1550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T04:25:30.000Z","msg":"幾時會出最高旅遊警示"}]}